!! Commonly-used types

* [WeakReference] - A strongly-typed, disposable replacement for MSDN's [url:WeakReference type|http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/system.weakreference.aspx].
* [WeakCollection] - A simple collection of weak references to objects.

!! Types used by implementation (exposed for convenience)

* [ObjectId] - A unique identifier and weak reference for an object instance.
* [IObjectIdReference] - A strongly-typed wrapper around [ObjectId].
* [ObjectTracker] - The component that creates [ObjectIds|ObjectId] and tracks the lifetimes of objects.